{"word":"ἐπηρεάζω","slug":"ἐπηρεάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπηρεάζω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to threaten abusively</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to deal despitefully with, act despitefully towards</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to be insolent</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἐπήρεια'><el>ἐπήρεια</el></a>\n"}]}